{"tid":1287230,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[五毛黨] 我宣告，分化撚全面進場","createTime":"2019-07-05T06:21:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T11:18:13.000Z","uid":270179,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"37f19667d8053ab77448cd848c340531ca80c06f","tid":1287230,"uid":270179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:21:57.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">雖然我係P牌仔，但大家可以自己決定我講嘢岩唔岩</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n之前五毛的分化方式係分化和理非同勇武<br />\n佢地不斷係連登、TG帶風向<br />\n分化議員、和理非同勇武派<br />\n但好彩大家經歷過雨傘血的教訓，就知道非要和理非同勇武派一齊合作不可<br />\n<br />\n不過五毛已經搵到真的分化點<br />\n就係聚焦香港同聲援中國<br />\n講真，見到咁多POST，就算話聲援中國的，都唔係話要攻打返上去，未又係話個日派下單張舉下牌咁大巴（而且見到想整單張個Ｄ人都唔係只想搞武漢，會想搞埋新彊、西藏、毒疫苗、姦女童幼稚園之類之類）<br />\n好多人都抱住分化強國人、膠膠地咩都試下的心情<br />\n講真個句，如果分化強國人呢招真係做唔起真係太柒，搞左一次就冇人會再搞啦<br />\n但有好多人帶風向講到D人係要打返上去、一係聲援中國一係聚焦香港，冇中間值<br />\n<br />\n各位諗返，我地係點樣走到而家<br />\n就係只要心中唔放棄五大訴求，不分化、不割席<br />\n就算唔認同其他兄弟的行動方式，或者覺得有D怪怪地、唔岩自己口味、唔適合自己都保持尊重，俾其他人試下lor（例如和理非集合、例如升級不合作運動、例如夢遊入去之類，總有人鍾意總有人唔鍾意）<br />\n自己唔鍾意就唔出聲、如果對方見冇人和應就做唔起<br />\n而家又要返去係網上互片，片到對方唔係人、唔跟住自己條路自己就要走！？！？！？！！！<br />\n係唔係又想俾人搞分化？<br />\n你都見到而家五毛勁多帶緊風向啦<br />\n唔鍾意人地咁樣搞就收聲，七月七日就帶多十塊五大訴求既牌、印多千幾張傳單去派！！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住心法<br />\n不分化<br />\n不割席<br />\n不篤灰<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做，互相支援</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kjO88Pb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkjO88Pb.jpg&h=e9111ac0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/873AOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F873AOPc.jpg&h=80cd9df5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yOsFfuc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyOsFfuc.png&h=a3676100&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/05/141842_1568e89c3160c354acbc9eda8c078eee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F05%2F141842_1568e89c3160c354acbc9eda8c078eee.png&h=87be1da6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r5yhhHy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr5yhhHy.png&h=7ee5362a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b23bc10e6bd496e84bda5513e603bc6b797c2d00","tid":1287230,"uid":23189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:24:04.000Z","msg":"「七黑」團結打倒白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284973\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284973</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zm1ytZc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzm1ytZc.jpg&h=68603869&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1edcbdaf00218cc12908e291fd86eaae55c6992","tid":1287230,"uid":270179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:25:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4rqrVwm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4rqrVwm.jpg&h=4feb7d68&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"baf7cb5ae6feeba46ebb45de006c931dbffacb6c","tid":1287230,"uid":200758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:26:16.000Z","msg":"五毛可以用武漢分化我地，我地都可以利用武漢將把火燒上大陸，但記住唔係幫武漢，77當日要集中係五大訴求先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f305d361c42d8961b3fe89e02891e4f6bde1fcd1","tid":1287230,"uid":270179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:27:23.000Z","msg":"自己推自己"},{"pid":"099cb7246edf070d89333047d73e60af99bfd190","tid":1287230,"uid":270179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:29:42.000Z","msg":"唔岩聽都要推自己"},{"pid":"6c14a85c8d70758b84fe436324e845901944b393","tid":1287230,"uid":214192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:31:52.000Z","msg":"自己屋企都未搞掂唔好插手人哋屋企住<br />\n香港仲叫有一國兩制同國際金融中心保住外國先會幫我哋出聲，但武漢真係純屬中國內政，外國理唔到太多<br />\n我哋做到嘅淨係想大陸人種植遊行示威呢啲概念，等佢哋返去慢慢發芽同開花"},{"pid":"24f0486fe19285fd8857e585173b1ba4e97c6d01","tid":1287230,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5487c07e7e63fd73a088a4d616593cdbf859194d","tid":1287230,"uid":42139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:34:37.000Z","msg":"巴打我都開左個POST講差唔多既意見...<br />\n留言者都算大部份支持但唔知點解好多DISLIKES...CLS<br />\n<br />\n只要強調返5大訴求, 其他兄弟想去做下野分化下大陸人都唔俾, 又話中國人唔係兄弟又成, 曲解個意思<br />\n<br />\n可能夜晚D人放左工, lihk先會正常D"},{"pid":"f11a260855eb73e46d2cbf85061caeae17c04e95","tid":1287230,"uid":270179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:35:04.000Z","msg":"我頂唔住頸<br />\n講真<br />\n我覺得講唔講武漢冇咩所謂<br />\n但唔好俾人分化到"},{"pid":"388ddabb771708b6f544b23759bad76de1ec751c","tid":1287230,"uid":270179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5487c07e7e63fd73a088a4d616593cdbf859194d","tid":1287230,"uid":42139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:34:37.000Z","msg":"巴打我都開左個POST講差唔多既意見...<br />\n留言者都算大部份支持但唔知點解好多DISLIKES...CLS<br />\n<br />\n只要強調返5大訴求, 其他兄弟想去做下野分化下大陸人都唔俾, 又話中國人唔係兄弟又成, 曲解個意思<br />\n<br />\n可能夜晚D人放左工, lihk先會正常D"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:36:34.000Z","msg":"我覺得dislike係帶風向<br />\n我相信同路人經歷左咁多野<br />\n會知道要包容自己唔鍾意的行動方式<br />\n<br />\n各有各做<br />\n唔好俾五毛三毛一毛半毛分化到！！！！"},{"pid":"0759ba803d22da19dea056e4b8b1bbdb49d04b51","tid":1287230,"uid":42139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"388ddabb771708b6f544b23759bad76de1ec751c","tid":1287230,"uid":270179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5487c07e7e63fd73a088a4d616593cdbf859194d","tid":1287230,"uid":42139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:34:37.000Z","msg":"巴打我都開左個POST講差唔多既意見...<br />\n留言者都算大部份支持但唔知點解好多DISLIKES...CLS<br />\n<br />\n只要強調返5大訴求, 其他兄弟想去做下野分化下大陸人都唔俾, 又話中國人唔係兄弟又成, 曲解個意思<br />\n<br />\n可能夜晚D人放左工, lihk先會正常D"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:36:34.000Z","msg":"我覺得dislike係帶風向<br />\n我相信同路人經歷左咁多野<br />\n會知道要包容自己唔鍾意的行動方式<br />\n<br />\n各有各做<br />\n唔好俾五毛三毛一毛半毛分化到！！！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:39:56.000Z","msg":"係, 同路人點做唔鍾意同唔同意都好，應該明白同體諒, 除非真係好走火入魔啦"},{"pid":"03f45c73cba9cb16aaa1d5dc65eb6bd3a7c2eb0c","tid":1287230,"uid":270179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:40:07.000Z","msg":"push自己"},{"pid":"aace692b89ef3f6432a1f2d689737db639e01c44","tid":1287230,"uid":270179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:46:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d7fLrLf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd7fLrLf.png&h=00fb19c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2183ab958d4850cf226cdd5f7fa57c88a98ff922","tid":1287230,"uid":270179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:56:18.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">唔係好明點會有人張聲援武漢同分化反送中運動拉埋黎講\n分你老母，同路人對抗極權勢力，你唔撚撐？\n其他國家既事唔關你事，當初籌旗外國傳媒報g20 果時你唔咁講？\n而家好難得搵到個機會去抗大反共勢力\n撐武漢唔撚係分化，多個朋友好過多個敵人呀屌\n咪盲反中反上腦 鄰國仲有好多人係清醒既，咪比五毛分化到 五毛係好撚中意分化中港兩地人 張所有反抗極權既意向抹黑為分裂國家\n佢地最怕就係你地搞到中國人都識團結反抗\n\n要用腦，唔好下下一黎就盲反得唔得，連登風向太易帶\n\n重申重點：\n五大訴求當然唔可以失焦，但撐武漢絕對唔係分化</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好俾人分化到<br />\n冇人話要反攻大陸<br />\n只係要燒佢後欄<br />\n不割席<br />\n不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n1.撤回條例<br />\n2.釋放義士<br />\n3.取消暴動定性<br />\n4.追究警方濫用武力鎮壓<br />\n5.落實雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HtoEwdk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHtoEwdk.png&h=45ccf763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Np0Z6F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Np0Z6F.png&h=d451cb32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/05/145107_1568e89c3160c354acbc9eda8c078eee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F05%2F145107_1568e89c3160c354acbc9eda8c078eee.png&h=2adf7012&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cc0ba7af39ad957cf13c3ccd735ba7aa51959b3","tid":1287230,"uid":270179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:10:42.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"d99aa5e04a8d91956fa9a06d7f2b1fccd48e107b","tid":1287230,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}